               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa ʾaślǝṭi, Lectionary for the entire year (fols. 1r-21v),
                     incomplete 
 
 Additio 1; colophon.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="5ra" to="58vb"/>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1917Mashaf#year">Maṣḥafa ʾaślǝṭi, Lectionary for the entire year</title>
                     <textLang xml:lang="gez"/>
                     
                     <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                        <locus target="#21v">21v</locus>: ተፈጸመ፡ በስምረተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ መጽሐፈ፡ አስሊጥ፡ ዘቤተ፡
                        ክርስቲያን። በዘመነ፡ ሉቃስ፡ በ፲፻ወ፱፻ወ፲ወ፩፡ ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት። በወርኃ፡ ግንቦት፡ በ፲፮፡ መዓልት፡ በ፳፩፡ ሠርቀ፡ ሌሊት።
                        በአልቦ፡ ጊዜ፡ ተወጥና፡ ወተፈጸመ። <note>The colophon states that the Ms. has been finished in
                        <date when="1919">Gǝnbot 16, 1911 year of mercy (= May 24, 1919 A.D.)</date>, in the time when there was
                        no king in Ethiopia: ba-zamana ʾalbo (nǝguś). </note>
                        <note>The text is called <title><foreign xml:lang="gez">አስሊጥ፡</foreign> ʾasliṭ</title> in the colophon. </note>
                     </colophon>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
               </msContents>
