                        <condition key="deficient">The Ms. is worn.
 The sewing has been crudely
                           repaired with synthetic threads.
 Some fols. are misplaced, some are
                           missing.
 Many fols. are damaged by water.
 The red ink is mostly
                           faded.</condition>
